    • Method Detail

      • addComponent

        void addComponent(net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.Component component)
        Add a component to the UI. If a tabbed UI was previously created by calling addTab(TabItemDisplay, Component), then the tabbed UI will be closed and any call to addTab(TabItemDisplay, Component) will create a new tabbed UI.
        Parameters:
        component - the component.

      • addNDEs

        void addNDEs(List<net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource.html.NDE> ndes)
        Add any NDEs required. Typically this will be basic CSS for using the editor. Make sure any CSS is specific to the editor UI.
        Parameters:
        ndes - NDE list.

      • addTab

        void addTab(net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.TabItemDisplay tabItemDisplay,
          net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.Component component)
        Add the component as a tab. If a tabbed UI was previously created by calling addTab(TabItemDisplay, Component), then the tabbed UI will have another tab added; otherwise a new tabbed UI will be created with the specified tab as the only tab.
        Parameters:
        tabItemDisplay - the tab item display.
        component - the component.

        the LocaleContext.

      • save

        boolean save()
        Save the editor UI. If the save is not successfully committed, any error messages will be sent to the configured notifiable. This should not be called by an Editor.
        Returns:
        true if the save was successfully committed.
